Introduction

Expense Tracker is a simple expense tracker app designed to help you manage your expenses efficiently. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your data while using our app.

Information We Collect

We do not collect any personal information or sensitive data about our users in Expense Tracker . The app solely stores and manages the expenses you manually input. The information you provide is stored locally on your device and is not transmitted to any external servers or third parties.

Permissions

Expense Tracker does not need any permissions.


How We Use Your Information

The information you input in Expense Tracker  is used solely for the purpose of tracking your expenses. We do not sell, share, or disclose this information to any third parties. Your data remains on your device and is not transmitted over the internet unless you choose to export or share it using the app's features.

Security

We take the security of your data seriously. 


Changes to this Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes to our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. The updated Privacy Policy will be effective immediately upon posting. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy regularly to stay informed about our data practices.

Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or the data practices of [Your App Name], please contact us at ivanfilonenko269@gmail.com.

By using Expense Tracker, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree with these terms, please do not use the app.

Thank you for using Expense Tracker. We appreciate your trust and are committed to protecting your privacy.
